Cyberpunk style: A towering holographic blueprint of interconnected geometric cubes and hexagonal nodes floats above a rain-slicked neon-lit cityscape at night. The structure resembles a complex web application architecture, with glowing data streams in electric blue and hot pink flowing between the nodes like digital synapses. In the foreground, a lone figure in a long coat stands on a rooftop, gazing up at the massive floating schematic, their silhouette reflected in puddles below. The architecture visualization pulses with energy, showing layers upon layers of interconnected frameworks building upon each other, creating something greater than its parts. Magenta and cyan light bathes the scene, with distant skyscrapers featuring animated billboards casting ambient glow through a light mist.
